Before Entering the Dojo Lessons
Namely, we will focusing on the following topics:
          What it means to code
          How to face errors

1. Organizing the Necessary Details
"Coding" is the process of thinking independently in order 
to find solutions.

2. Facing and Overcoming Errors
Errors can be solved by reading the details.

It is important to check the details of the error message 
displayed in the browser.
There are also hints in the error messages

The error message also displays where the error occurred.

If you are encountering errors, try following the steps below:
          Read the error details carefully
          If you cannot understand the error, do a web search on the error message